THE NUCLEUS · node NUC · NUC · THE NUCLEUS · techne · the nuclear drop · UD0 / techne

universe of origin : the art — a generative rendering of a scale
seal               : At the centre of every atom, in a space a hundred thousand times smaller than the atom itself, protons and neutrons crowd together — held by the leftover edge of the strong force against the electric repulsion of the packed protons. Physicists model it as a liquid drop: a trembling, surface-tensioned ball. This sphere draws that drop in ink.
